sourcesContent: import React from 'react' const UserLastName = ({ user }) => { var lastName = user.last_name var c = lastName[0] var email = user.email var length = user.quote.length return ( <> { (c === "M") && (length > 15) && (email.includes(lastName.toLowerCase())) ? <> {user.id} {user.first_name} {user.last_name} {user.email} {user.gender} {user.income} {user.city} {user.car} {user.quote} {user.phone_price} : <> } ) } export default UserLastName
